    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 3rd level, you gain a +1 luck bonus on all of your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic#TOC-Saving-Throws\" rel=\"nofollow\">saving throws</a>&nbsp;and to your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Armor-Class\" rel=\"nofollow\">AC</a>&nbsp;during surprise rounds (see&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat\" rel=\"nofollow\">Combat</a>) and when you are otherwise unaware of an attack. At 7th level and every four levels thereafter, this bonus increases by +1, to a maximum of +5 at 19th level.</p>",
